snippet.title: NAMCO MUSEUM Arcade PAC - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Take your favorite arcade classics on the go with NAMCO MUSEUM Arcade PAC! Arriving exclusively for the Nintendo Switch on September 28th!
